---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ubicación" description="Cómo llegar al Hostal Tambococha en Catacocha, Loja. Ubicación, rutas en auto y bus desde Loja y Guayaquil, y puntos de interés cercanos.">
    <section class="bg-background-light py-12 md:py-16 pt-24 md:pt-32 px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-20 text-center border-b border-earth/10">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <span class="mb-4 inline-block rounded-full bg-sage/10 px-4 py-1 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sage">Nuestra Ubicación</span>
            <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight text-earth">Encuéntranos en <span class="italic text-primary">Catacocha</span></h1>
            <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-relaxed text-earth/80 font-medium max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                En el corazón de la Sierra Sur del Ecuador: a 97 km de Loja y a solo tres horas del Perú. Hostal Tambococha te ofrece una ubicación privilegiada para descubrir los paisajes de la provincia.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-20 py-12">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-12">
            <div class="w-full lg:w-[40%] space-y-10">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-earth mb-8">Cómo Llegar</h2>
                    
                    <!-- Subsección 1: En Auto -->
                    <div class="mb-6">
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-earth/50 mb-4 px-2 border-l-2 border-primary">En Auto</h3>
                        <div class="space-y-6">
                            
                            <!-- Desde Loja (Auto) -->
                            <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">directions_car</span>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-earth text-lg">Desde Loja</h4>
                                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-2">
                                        <span class="bg-earth/5 text-earth/80 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold border border-earth/10">97 km</span>
                                        <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold border border-primary/20">2 hrs aprox.</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-earth/70 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-1 font-medium">Carretera Panamericana / Troncal de la Sierra / E35.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Desde Guayaquil (Auto) -->
                            <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">directions_car</span>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-earth text-lg">Desde Guayaquil</h4>
                                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 my-2">
                                        <span class="bg-earth/5 text-earth/80 text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold border border-earth/10">350 km</span>
                                        <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold border border-primary/20">6,5 hrs aprox.</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <p class="text-earth/70 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-1 font-medium">Troncal de la Costa/E25 y Transversal Sur/E50 hacia Loja.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="w-full h-px bg-earth/10 my-6"></div>

                    <!-- Subsección 2: En Bus -->
                    <div>
                        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-earth/50 mb-4 px-2 border-l-2 border-primary">En Bus</h3>
                        <div class="space-y-6">
                            
                            <!-- Desde Terminal Terrestre de Loja (Bus) -->
                            <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">directions_bus</span>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-earth text-lg leading-tight mb-1">Desde Terminal Terrestre de Loja</h4>
                                    <p class="text-earth/80 text-sm font-bold mb-2">Cooperativas: <span class="font-normal">Loja Internacional / Unión Cariamanga.</span></p>
                                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                        <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold border border-sage/20">$3,5 USD aprox.</span>
                                        <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold border border-primary/20">2,5 hrs aprox.</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <!-- Desde Guayaquil (Bus) -->
                            <div class="flex gap-4 group">
                                <div class="flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">directions_bus</span>
                                </div>
                                <div>
                                    <h4 class="font-bold text-earth text-lg mb-2">Desde Guayaquil</h4>
                                    <p class="text-earth/80 text-sm font-bold mb-2">Cooperativas: <span class="font-normal">Loja Internacional.</span></p>
                                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                                        <span class="bg-sage/10 text-sage text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold border border-sage/20">$15 USD aprox.</span>
                                        <span class="bg-primary/10 text-primary text-xs px-2 py-1 rounded font-bold border border-primary/20">6,5 hrs aprox.</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <a href="https://maps.app.goo.gl/sqTERKTazBKp2cPe8" target="_blank" class="w-full bg-earth text-white py-4 rounded-xl font-bold flex items-center justify-center gap-2 hover:bg-earth/90 transition-all shadow-lg shadow-earth/20">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">map</span>
                    Abrir en Google Maps
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="w-full lg:w-[60%] min-h-[300px] md:min-h-[500px] flex">
                <div class="w-full h-[400px] md:h-[600px] bg-slate-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative">
                    <iframe title="Mapa de ubicación del Hostal Tambococha en Google Maps" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3979.8551660484086!2d-79.6511403290452!3d-4.049952357094313!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x9034c6d3387011f7%3A0x3254d569c65d612e!2sHotel%20Tambococha!5e0!3m2!1ses!2scl!4v1772732117092!5m2!1ses!2scl" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="bg-white py-12 md:py-16 px-4 md:px-6 lg:px-20 border-t border-earth/10">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-earth mb-10 flex items-center gap-3">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sage">explore</span>
                Puntos Cercanos
            </h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
                <!-- Tarjeta 1 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col p-6 bg-background-light rounded-xl border border-earth/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all cursor-default group">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="text-sage group-hover:text-primary transition-colors flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">landscape</span>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-earth text-lg leading-tight">Mirador Shiriculapo</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-earth/60 mb-6 flex-grow">Mirador natural emblemático de la ciudad.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-sage mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-earth/5">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">directions_car</span>
                        4 min. de viaje
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Tarjeta 2 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col p-6 bg-background-light rounded-xl border border-earth/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all cursor-default group">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="text-sage group-hover:text-primary transition-colors flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">park</span>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-earth text-lg leading-tight">Parque Central</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-earth/60 mb-6 flex-grow">Centro histórico y arquitectura colonial.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-sage mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-earth/5">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">directions_walk</span>
                        1 min. caminando
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Tarjeta 3 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col p-6 bg-background-light rounded-xl border border-earth/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all cursor-default group">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="text-sage group-hover:text-primary transition-colors flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">church</span>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-earth text-lg leading-tight">Iglesia Matriz</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-earth/60 mb-6 flex-grow">Patrimonio cultural religioso de la zona.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-sage mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-earth/5">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">directions_walk</span>
                        1 min. caminando
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Tarjeta 4 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col p-6 bg-background-light rounded-xl border border-earth/5 hover:border-primary/30 transition-all cursor-default group">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
                        <div class="text-sage group-hover:text-primary transition-colors flex-shrink-0">
                            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">restaurant</span>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="font-bold text-earth text-lg leading-tight">Mercado Municipal</h4>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-earth/60 mb-6 flex-grow">Los mejores platos típicos lojanos.</p>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-bold text-sage mt-auto pt-4 border-t border-earth/5">
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">directions_walk</span>
                        3 min. caminando
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
